{"tid":1458621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領機場，機場巴士司機係最重要","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:48:46.000Z","uid":96346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eadeffabfa6ddc188ffed204c17bba8106f376b3","tid":1458621,"uid":96346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"如果你識人或你自己係，唔該通知佢<br />\n<br />\n首先今日真係走到走唔到<br />\n行路去東涌其實係下策<br />\n萬一機場快線站停埋後果不堪設想<br />\n所以對於困係孤島既人<br />\n機場巴士司機係唯一可以拯救到大家既人<br />\n車既數目又多載客量又高<br />\n緊急情況下目的地更可自由更改<br />\n猶如一支大型保姆車隊<br />\n<br />\n希望你地係緊急情況下做<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">逆權司機</span></strong><br />\n係呢個機場疏散既漏洞入面<br />\n你地係最可以幫到我地"},{"pid":"ff6cd0f7f779c0d747f08858d6b3a1ece421926a","tid":1458621,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得太多post太亂？我整左個策略、行動、文宣方向精華集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1444217/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7AT6Db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7AT6Db.png&h=b6163964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">機場檢討POST懶人包</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458355/page/1</a><br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458321/page/1</a><br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457623/page/1</a><br />\n我覺得今日散水無錯，互屌先係真中計<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457903/page/1</a><br />\n[賽後檢討] 今日機場有無散水既都麻煩入一入黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457735/page/1</a><br />\n下次搞再機場唔該幫下啲旅客<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457517/page/1</a><br />\n今日機場事件有少少諗法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1457187/page/1</a><br />\n我係散水撚，我係嚟道歉嘅</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n好需要你幫手報料/update/宣傳呀"},{"pid":"55b40a24be459f45b102f045c7d8f39f916e1f1f","tid":1458621,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"發夢沿路見到都好塞... 巴士都入唔到機場接人走..."},{"pid":"a33ac75c4ee4f8b718ee61d25347091e512bc5f5","tid":1458621,"uid":96346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55b40a24be459f45b102f045c7d8f39f916e1f1f","tid":1458621,"uid":10125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"發夢沿路見到都好塞... 巴士都入唔到機場接人走..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"如果下次真係清場時間未必塞，到時真係需要車"}]}